  "description": {
   "en": "On the eve of the Pacific War.\n\nFukuhara Yuusaku, a Kobe-based trader, goes to Manchuria in search of supplies and discovers a startling national secret.\n\nYuusaku, out of a sense of justice, decides to disclose it to the world, but his wife, Satoko...\n\nA romance/suspense hidden in the fires of war.\n\nWinner of the Silver Lion at the 77th Venice International Film Festival.\nFirst manga adaptation of Kurosawa Kiyoshi's film."
